data.description: Adorable Home in a Amazing Neighborhood! The community pool, park and tennis/basketball courts are just a block away from your front door and the homeowner's association holds several social events at the park throughout the year. This home has so much to offer, wood laminate flooring and wood blinds in the living room and New Granite Countertops! The spacious living room has a high ceiling, built-in bookshelves/cabinets surrounding the wood burning fireplace & lots of natural light. Large Prep area and Kitchen Cabinet Storage.You will find the split bedroom floor plan offers a little more privacy. Have you been hoping for a master bedroom with a separate sitting area, office or nursery space? We have it here in this nice sized master suite with private bathroom that includes a whirlpool tub, separate shower, double sink vanity and walk-in closet. Enjoy time with family and friends in the large fenced back yard or on the covered patio. New Trane A/C & Roof in 2020.This home should definitely be on your "must see" list. Call to schedule your viewing appointment today!
